@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xmxmzf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.50) + wp.abs(v2 + 0.12)) + (0.55 - (v0 + 0.35 + v0 + 0.19)))
    tmp = (v2 - v1)
    v2 = wp.cos(v2)
    tmp = wp.exp(v1)
    v0 = 0.12
    v1 = wp.abs((tmp * wp.sin(v2 + 0.69)))
    data[tid] = v0
